Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:15.93,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(212,117.667)}Korekcia:\NHaany
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:19.93,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(212,117.667)}Titulky od GAW-Subs\Nwww.gawsubs.com\N2015
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:16.94,Default,Sa,0,0,0,,Tak poďme vyriešiť túto záhadu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:33.97,Default,Hanabusa,0,0,0,,Vitaj
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:35.83,Default,Hanabusa,0,0,0,,v priepasti.
